description: The ceremony marking Isle of Man's national day has been reduced in size due to the coronavirus pandemic.
title: Scaled back Tynwald ceremony marks Isle of Man national day
title_page: Scaled back Tynwald ceremony marks Isle of Man national day - BBC News
maintext: "We always come to Tynwald and we just thought it would be a historic occasion this year to actually see it without all the fair, just quite quiet and just seeing the bits of the ceremony that are left, the official part."
